><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U M U M' U M U M\">U M U M' U M U M</span></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/roux-eolr/zh/image58.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/roux-eolr/zh/image60.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/roux-eolr/zh/image62.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/roux-eolr/zh/image64.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/roux-eolr/zh/image66.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>M*让LR到U, U*让另一LR到它对面, M*藏另一LR -&gt; 叠3/1 (M U M'; M' U M')</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p>U*, M*平D层LR -&gt; 准备LR (U M')</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p>M*: U*让D层LR到U层LR -&gt; 好3/1 (M U' M')</p></td><td><p>U', M*: U*让坏LR到D层好棱 -&gt; 好3/1 (U' M' U M)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>UF分离 (上坏, 下)</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p>侧</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p>UF相对</p></td><td><p>底</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>U M' U M' U M U M'; </p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U M U M' U' M U' M'\">U M U M' U' M U' M'</span></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U M' U' M' U2 M U' M U\">U M' U' M' U2 M U' M U</span></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"M' U M' U' M U' M' U2 M U M' U2\">M' U M' U' M U' M' U2 M U M' U2</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"M' U M U M' U M U M' U M' U\">M' U M U M' U M U M' U M' U</span></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/roux-eolr/zh/image68.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/roux-eolr/zh/image70.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/roux-eolr/zh/image72.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/roux-e